BT /F1 10.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 355.50 Tm (Five cards: Config Server, Service Registry, API Gateway, Distributed Tracing, Circuit Breaker.) Tj ET
0.720 0.720 0.760 rg 58.00 342.00 3.00 35.50 re f
BT /F2 9.50 Tf 0.040 0.340 0.780 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 331.00 Tm (SAY \(read this aloud\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 315.00 Tm (Across every real microservices system, the same five patterns show up. Each one solves a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 299.80 Tm (specific headache. We will actually build the first two today, and just understand the other three -) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 284.60 Tm (you will meet all of them on real projects. Let me give you each one with its problem and its fix.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 264.40 Tm (Config Server - the problem: ten services means ten separate config files to manage. The fix: one) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 249.20 Tm (central, shared config. Service Registry - the problem: services start on changing ports and you) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 234.00 Tm (cannot hard-code addresses. The fix: a live phonebook of what is running where. API Gateway -) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 218.80 Tm (the problem: callers should not need to know all your internal addresses. The fix: one single front) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 203.60 Tm (door. Distributed Tracing - the problem: a request hops through five services and one is slow, but) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 188.40 Tm (which? The fix: end-to-end tracking. And Circuit Breaker - the problem: service B is down and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 173.20 Tm (service A keeps hammering it. The fix: detect the failure, stop calling, return a fallback.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 153.00 Tm (So today we build the Service Registry and the API Gateway. The other three, we will understand) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 137.80 Tm (by concept. Knowing all five, and what each solves, is what matters.) Tj ET
